Description copied from interface: User
Holds information about the state of the market for a given stock, i.e, where the stock is trading, that is of interest to a User. The information includes that name of the stock, and the bid and offer prices and quantities.

Specified by:
acceptCurrentMarket in interface User
Parameters:
product - Symbol of the stock
bp - Buy price of the stock, i.e, the bid
bv - Buy volume of the stock i.e., how much is available for buying
sp - Selling price of the stock, i.e., the offer
sv - Sell volume of the stock, i.e., how much is available for selling
